item.title: response to Thespoian
item.description: 18:44 Wednesday 11 March 2015 JST for each kind of nonce What does “nonce” mean in this context? I thought it was a single-use secret number, but it looks like you mean token.. ?? select the method based on tokens present Basically that’s what I did: put tokens in the string and make the script brute force through every combination, substituting values in from lists.
